{"tid":1390512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請 注 意 ! 我地要來一場  「媒體輿論大反擊 ! 」","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:23:04.000Z","uid":270860,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a888a84886acd2986c67ce07ed8c28dc9c936cf0","tid":1390512,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"(注意) (請廣傳、齊幫手!)<br />\n<br />\n中共一直抹黑反送中運動係外國勢力裏應外合、民陣搞港獨，示威者係街頭暴徒等等...<br />\n<br />\n一直妖魔化我地嘅運動，令13億人同香港700萬人互相對立，目的就係要孤立我地嘅運動， 令中港兩地共同嘅敵人 - 中共習近平， 可以更易打碎我地嘅民主運動。<br />\n<br />\n小弟最近發現中共防火長城有漏洞！由於香港電台作為「政府官方媒體」所以網站仲未被block！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地係時候，進行一場媒體輿論<br />\n大反擊! <br />\n<br />\n大量share 港台新聞同節目比大陸親友 ! 特別係駭人聽聞既元朗恐襲事件！認清獨裁政權，團結中港民眾！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkcc/episode/579157?fbclid=IwAR1eCU5mnJGRl_puRT4VW5VWBkXT-5XLkG0yoSv-0hcsFh2eR2qngVVxPas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhkcc%2Fepisode%2F579157%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1eCU5mnJGRl_puRT4VW5VWBkXT-5XLkG0yoSv-0hcsFh2eR2qngVVxPas&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qncFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=86fe927b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkcc/episode/579157?fbclid=IwAR1eCU5mnJGRl_puRT4VW5VWBkXT-5XLkG0yoSv-0hcsFh2eR2qngVVxPas</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zGHaoL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGHaoL4.jpg&h=13e0306a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LnfOUSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnfOUSL.jpg&h=22e8c736&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dca83b1be4ed720d91a4f74f8eadef1b8b571ea","tid":1390512,"uid":270860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c74bf2b3a1b9ed6d92e05f4520fab5b2be4f62b","tid":1390512,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:15:57.000Z","msg":"[重開免會員版] 呢個師奶要求黑警出示委任證，黑警差少少就開槍殺死個師奶<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<